node.text: #NEWS: We have surpassed 500 installations of the @InmarsatGlobal Jet ConneX in-flight connectivity platform on large-cabin aircraft. The robust Wi-Fi solution is available on new aircraft and can be retrofitted on qualifying existing aircraft. #ArtOfExcellence

node.text: We just delivered the final commercial #G550. During its nearly two decades in service, the G550 set a new standard for performance and reliability and continues to outperform and impress with its wide-ranging capabilities. #ArtOfExcellence

node.text: To new heights — each look at the sky is a reminder of opportunity. #FanFriday by @alangrubelic.

node.text: The already industry-leading Gulfstream G700 is now even better, with a new, lower cabin altitude. Read more about the G700's improved cabin experience at the #linkinbio.

node.text: A mile of runway will take you anywhere. Reach your "anywhere" even sooner in the ultralong-range #G650ER. You simply can't fly farther faster. #ArtOfExcellence
